@GatewayHost = http://localhost:5000

# =============================================================================
# SEED DATA — MediTrack Local
# Ejecutar EN ORDEN. Algunos registros dependen de IDs creados anteriormente.
# Pacientes: 1 = Carlos Mendoza, 2 = Ana Torres, 3 = Luis García
#
# ORDEN:
#   Treatment 1-3  → crea catálogo (IDs 1,2,3)
#   Treatment 4-5  → crea recetas  (doseScheduleIds 1,2,3)
#   Appointment 1-5
#   Followup 1-5
#   Analysis 1-5
#   Reminder 1-5   → independientes, cualquier orden
# =============================================================================

### [Treatment 1/5] Agregar Metformina al catálogo
POST {{GatewayHost}}/treatment/api/v1/medication-catalog
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "officialName": "Metformina 500mg",
  "synonyms": "Glucophage, Dimefor",
  "category": "Antidiabético"
}

### [Treatment 2/5] Agregar Atorvastatina al catálogo
POST {{GatewayHost}}/treatment/api/v1/medication-catalog
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "officialName": "Atorvastatina 20mg",
  "synonyms": "Lipitor, Torvast",
  "category": "Hipolipemiante"
}

### [Treatment 3/5] Agregar Losartán al catálogo
POST {{GatewayHost}}/treatment/api/v1/medication-catalog
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "officialName": "Losartán 50mg",
  "synonyms": "Cozaar, Lortaan",
  "category": "Antihipertensivo"
}

### [Treatment 4/5] Receta paciente 1 (Carlos) — Metformina catalogId=1 → doseScheduleIds 1,2
POST {{GatewayHost}}/treatment/api/v1/prescriptions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": 1,
  "technicalStaffId": 10,
  "notes": "Tomar con las comidas. Control en 30 días.",
  "medications": [
    {
      "catalogId": 1,
      "dose": "500mg",
      "frequencyHours": 12,
      "startDate": "2026-06-24T00:00:00",
      "endDate": "2026-09-24T00:00:00",
      "stockCount": 60,
      "stockAlertThreshold": 10,
      "doseSchedules": [
        { "scheduledTime": "08:00:00" },
        { "scheduledTime": "20:00:00" }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### [Treatment 5/5] Receta paciente 2 (Ana) — Atorvastatina + Losartán → doseScheduleIds 3,4
